rComments: Vraiment un bon prof. Plusieurs travaux d'équipe alors choisissez des personnes fiables. Les travaux étaient assez simple. Aucun examen de mis-session. Il y avait des travaux de compréhension de lecture (x2), travaux d'équipe pour des points de participation (x6), exposé orale en équipe (20% de la note finale) et un travail de fin session (seule).
teacherRatingTags: ['Get ready to read', 'Participation matters', 'Lots of homework']

rComments: His class is fun, but we unfortunately don't learn a lot about filming, more about video editing (which I was okay with). I loved his class tho! If you show that you care and that you're present, he will give you good grades. The assignments can be exhaustive but they're interesting and I learned a lot about video editing. He takes the attendances!

Ce professeur manque de dynamisme dans son enseignement. Il lit ses PowerPoints, difficiles à saisir en les relisant, à cause des nombreuses fautes de structure de phrases. Il présente des vidéos à TOUS les cours, qui à mon avis, ne sont pas toujours pertinentes. Or, il n'est pas trop sévère dans sa correction et le travail final est très simple.
Très gentil professeur, passionné, qui se soucie de ses élèves. Il parlera beaucoup de la photographie en général.
He's actually a great prof. His midterm is straightforward and pretty simple if you go over the slides a few times. There aren't any surprises. Overall, I would recommend him.

Not an easy class, very unclear expectations. The requirements for exams and assignments are never stated - makes passing the class, let alone receiving a good grade, extremely unlikely. Would not take again. He's a nice guy though.
Il me fait penser à Grand papa bi de passe partout.
Great sense of humor! He loves teaching and it shows
Terrible teaching. The tech assistant was the one doing most of the teaching and was much more useful. Never again.

One of those rare teachers that acts as a guide instead of cramming information down your throat. If you want to put effort into learning for yourself take his class if you'd rather be spoon fead take another one.
I loved this teacher. He was just simple, interesting and to the point. He knows what he's doing and loves the students. I think he is great in what he does, just loved his class.
Very Good course!  Great humor, interesting and understanding.  Great knowledge in the field and does what he can to make you succeed.
Il est etrange ce prof, sympathique mais il reponds toujours par "c'est difficle" ou par une autre question. Bref pas beaucoup de solution. Je sais pas si on apprendra beaucoup.
